FBIS3-44928 "drchi007_e_94012" FBIS-CHI-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 Southeast Asia & Pacific Australian Broadcasting Agreement Signed OW0701144894 Beijing XINHUA in English 1436 GMT 7 Jan 94 OW0701144894 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, January 7 (XINHUA) -- Sino-Australian broadcasting agreement was signed here this evening by Ai Zhisheng, China's minister for radio, film and television, and David Hill, managing director of Australian Broadcasting Corporation. David Hill arrived here on January 5 at the invitation of the Chinese Ministry of Radio, Film and Television.
